    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver or a great project for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the hood and a few minor door dings, while the interior has moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will eventually need a suspension refresh and a new set of tires to be perfect. It has been recently serviced with an oil change and a new battery, and it passed its last emissions test without issue.",
